{"tid":2151781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方：對部分傳媒抹黑搜查行動十分遺憾","createTime":"2020-08-11T14:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T17:08:46.000Z","uid":20933,"like":16,"dislike":241,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"6a803080e0ade3feb733dd3eeee7f183371cc545","tid":2151781,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:35:00.000Z","msg":"警方表示，昨日拘捕壹傳媒集團創辦人黎智英等人的行動，完全是依法進行，保障國家安全，強調行動針對的是被捕人涉嫌干犯的違法行為，並非個別傳媒機構，又指警方行動前已提醒警員避免觸及採訪資料，蒐證時亦多次出示搜查令，並在壹傳媒的人員陪同下進行，對於有部分傳媒刻意抹黑警方的搜查行動，表示十分遺憾。 <br />\n<br />\n警方又指，昨日讓部份傳媒進入封鎖區採訪，是希望增加警務工作透明度，警方完全理解部份傳媒機構或記者持不同意見，會充分聽取傳媒意見後，檢討和改善安排。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2351738\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2351738&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=47869e50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2351738</a>"},{"pid":"31a557f65b74c93de7f12cfc6b9a0cb3674fcbfb","tid":2151781,"uid":76745,"like":103,"dislike":0,"score":103,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:36:14.000Z","msg":"係呀全世界抹黑你 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e414f467613bb9c173077812689d3dcc3b3c935","tid":2151781,"uid":51271,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"quote":{"pid":"31a557f65b74c93de7f12cfc6b9a0cb3674fcbfb","tid":2151781,"uid":76745,"like":103,"dislike":0,"score":103,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:36:14.000Z","msg":"係呀全世界抹黑你 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:37:00.000Z","msg":"影住你亂揭，仲想spin?"},{"pid":"bfa8a8431893e8a1c8ab8c67ddd09bd297c4c469","tid":2151781,"uid":159392,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"含撚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642c5ffb580ce8466bc611cb38762b37b6595aaa","tid":2151781,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:40:15.000Z","msg":